About
The LINQ Promenade is Caesars Entertainment's shopping, dining and entertainment district located at the center of the Las Vegas Strip which is home to 35+ restaurant and retail stores such as Brooklyn Bowl, Gordon Ramsay Fish and Chips, IN-N-Out Burger, Razer, Yard House, and so much more! You can find exciting attractions at The LINQ Promenade such as The High Roller, North America's Tallest Observation wheel, and Fly LINQ Zipline, the strip's only zipline. There's something for everyone at The LINQ Promenade!
Duration: 2-3 hours

Not great!!
Sep 2024 • Couples
The Linq was just ok. The shower is horrible. The shower area is so small with a big rain showerhead so you have to place the showerhead in a totally upright position to wash and shampoo. No room to move around at all!! There was mold around the dispense machines in the shower which of course we didn't use. We went to the pool one day and rented a beach bed for $75 and had to buy $50 in food or drink which is no problem as 2 drinks pretty much come out to $50. The problem was when it was time to leave we could not find our server for our check and nobody else said they could get it for us which I find ridiculous. When I finally found her after literally 45 minutes she said she was busy with bottle service for someone else. If that takes 45 minutes, someone else should be able to hand me my bill to let me pay and leave. I would not stay here again!

The LINQ Promenade is in the heart of Vegas
Jun 2024 • Friends
The LINQ Promenade is a popular open-air shopping, dining and entertainment district with 35+ restaurants, shops and some lovely fountains.

Gordon Ramsay Fish & Chips is a popular British-themed counter-serve pub style food; using sustainable true cod and coated with custard powder batter for the perfect golden crisp. @gordonramsayfishandchips

I Love Sugar is much more than a candy store. They have every type of candy imaginable. With dream-like creativity, it’s the largest candy store in the world!! They also have the Candy Martini Bar upstairs. Make reservations. @ilovesugar @candymartinibar

In-N-Out Burger has possibly the best deal on the Strip. @inandoutvegas

Flamingo
See the flamingos, unique bird species and exotic fish🦩@flamingovegas

The High Roller is a 550 foot observation wheel. The 28 air-conditioned passenger cabins are enclosed by handcrafted Italian glass, where one revolution takes about 30 minutes. @highrollervegas
